            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. Google's Responsive Display and Meta's Dynamic Creative make DCO usable at any budget. Full-featured platforms like Smartly.io and Celtra are better suited to advertisers spending $25,000+ per month.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
